el des begegnungsorientierten Konzepts - im Geographieunterricht eingeübt werden kann.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 25. Jul 2018) 4aAtmosphere. 4aAtmosphäre. 4aBildung. 4aBildungsforschung. 4aBildungssoziologie. 4aEducation. 4aEducational Research. 4aInterculturalism. 4aInterkulturalität. 4aMigration. 4aPedagogy. 4aPädagogik. 4aRaum. 4aSociology of Education. 4aSpace.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Social Sciences 2018z9783110603231oZDB-23-DSW40uhttps://doi.org/10.14361/9783839443453zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783839443453.jpg  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2017  aZDB-23-DSWb2018